itemdescription_propertiesrulesetname: The name of the rule set containing the rule.
itemdescription_propertiesorder: The order in which the rules are applied for the endpoint. Possible values {0,1,2,3,………}. A rule with a lesser order will be applied before a rule with a greater order. Rule with order 0 is a special rule. It does not require any condition and actions listed in it will always be applied.
itemdescription_propertiesconditions: A list of conditions that must be matched for the actions to be executed
itemdescription_propertiesactions: A list of actions that are executed when all the conditions of a rule are satisfied.
itemdescription_propertiesmatchprocessin: If this rule is a match should the rules engine continue running the remaining rules or stop. If not present, defaults to Continue.
